{"id":151997,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/新翻译工具将揭示海豚的语言/","date":"2011-05-13T00:30:45Z","modified":"2011-05-13T02:20:11Z","title":"新翻译工具将揭示海豚的“语言”","content":"<p>野生海豚项目创始人Denise Herzing与乔治亚理工学院人工智能研究员Thad Starner合作，建立名为“鲸类听觉和遥测（CHAT）”的项目，目的是在海豚的帮助下共同创造一门语言，并最终用于解释海豚的自然语言，实现两个物种之间的交流。 Herzing和Starner将在年中开始用他们发明的设备原型测试野生海豚。首先潜水员将向海豚播放研究人员杜撰的八个单词，意思指海草，或弓或海浪。然后，软件监听海豚是否有没有模仿这些单词。一旦系统识别出模仿单词，他们将开始监听海豚的自然声音，寻找出海豚交流中“基本单元”，解释其语言意义。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14c6836b/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%96%B0%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%B0%86%E6%8F%AD%E7%A4%BA%E6%B5%B7%E8%B1%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F12%2F0748216%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%96%B0%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%B0%86%E6%8F%AD%E7%A4%BA%E6%B5%B7%E8%B1%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F12%2F0748216%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092115509/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14c6836b/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092115509/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14c6836b/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=2ztUP8PH_po:ZQg5IYqhWGc:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=2ztUP8PH_po:ZQg5IYqhWGc:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q7